<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 - Page non trouvée | SyncBoard</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .error-container {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #1a1a1a;
        background-image: linear-gradient(
          to bottom right,
          rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2) 0%,
          transparent 100%
        );
        position: relative;
      }

      .error-content {
        background: #262626;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 90%;
        border: 1px solid #404040;
      }

      .error-icon {
        font-size: 4rem;
        color: #4f46e5;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .error-content h1 {
        font-size: 6rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #e5e7eb;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .error-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: #9ca3af;
        margin: 1rem 0;
      }

      .error-content p {
        color: #9ca3af;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .error-content .btn-primary {
        background: #4f46e5;
        color: #e5e7eb;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.8rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        border: none;
      }

      .error-content .btn-primary:hover {
        background: #4338ca;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .error-content {
          padding: 2rem;
        }

        .error-content h1 {
          font-size: 4rem;
        }

        .error-content h2 {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="error-container">
      <div class="error-content">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle error-icon"></i>
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Page non trouvée</h2>
        <p>La page que vous recherchez n'existe pas ou a été déplacée.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-primary">
          <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
          Retour à l'accueil
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
